rrer\"><div><div>边际效应与杠杆 | Talk about DAO 0x05</div><div>解决「迷思」：BuidlerDAO 如何处理「外部开发任务」？</div><div><div><img src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/a/wx_fed/assets/res/MjliNWVm.svg?t=e3654e80-f904-41f7-aa9a-19887747b145\" alt=\"边际效应与杠杆 | Talk about DAO 0x05\"></div><div>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTM0MzE5Mw==&amp;mid=2247486365&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=338ce3dccb0771fe17a10f6778ffb7b2&amp;chksm=e94ebd2bde39343d5c4ae627a27168e2d81364999947bf5a34f20fca8b9490d6f9a713441aa0&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect</div></div></div><div><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UrYDA9tqpqVQ0hzib8lcickjJiadwAUxEkibUYv3AicdAUGYmCN9XxDMVibCB4dLA8fT3t0JyppzGwDI9lAzJvtnGlBw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;t=e3654e80-f904-41f7-aa9a-19887747b145\" alt=\"边际效应与杠杆 | Talk about DAO 0x05\"></div></a></div><div><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTM0MzE5Mw==&amp;mid=2247486299&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=51549df702d61fb6408725f4a646ba34&amp;chksm=e94ebdedde3934fb468bf3a5f2bb4fae918a6f31f7e2227a0bb96b1d77d2b5be7ad2d49513bb&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><div><div>以个体成长为导向的任务投放 | Talk about DAO 0x04</div><div>将成员的个人成长作为「最重要的目标」，将「组织发展」放在其后</div><div><div><img src=\"https://res.wx.qq.com/a/wx_fed/assets/res/MjliNWVm.svg?t=4701dc01-e4e2-4055-956e-24d7a757f9dd\" alt=\"以个体成长为导向的任务投放 | Talk about DAO 0x04\"></div><div>https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTM0MzE5Mw==&amp;mid=2247486299&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=51549df702d61fb6408725f4a646ba34&amp;chksm=e94ebdedde3934fb468bf3a5f2bb4fae918a6f31f7e2227a0bb96b1d77d2b5be7ad2d49513bb&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect</div></div></div><div><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/UrYDA9tqpqWRqvCRiaWXZBWCxwFicz0zcfLPlPmx7C3k9maan99tIicKzicPYg41IJKaXnU8PsNib00pfrasUBxmUJQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;t=4701dc01-e4e2-4055-956e-24d7a757f9dd\" alt=\"以个体成长为导向的任务投放 | Talk about DAO 0x04\"></div></a></div><div><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NTM0MzE5Mw==&amp;mid=2247486287&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8218c8d5abf37ea2ee9a69207c2c630c&amp;chksm=e94ebdf9de3934ef17e